<inglise> Whereas: </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) In November 1999, the International Council for the Exploration of the Sea (ICES) indicated that the stock of cod in the Irish Sea (ICES division VIIa) is at a serious risk of collapse. </inglise>
<eesti> 1) 1999. aasta novembris m&auml;rkis Rahvusvaheline Mereuurimise N&otilde;ukogu (ICES), et Iiri mere (ICES VIIa rajoon) tursavarud on suures ohus; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) The advice from ICES also indicated that the quantity of mature cod in the Irish Sea would remain at a very low level during 2000 and 2001. </inglise>
<eesti> 2) ICESi n&otilde;uandes m&auml;rgitakse samuti, et Iiri mere suguk&uuml;pse tursa kogus j&auml;&auml;b aastatel 2000 ja 2001 v&auml;ga v&auml;ikeseks; </eesti>
<inglise> (3) Commission Regulation (EC) No 304/2000 of 9 February 2000 establishing measures for the recovery of the stock of cod in the Irish Sea (ICES division VIIa) (3) put in place measures to protect adult cod during the spawning season of 2000. </inglise>
