<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> The authorities of Member States shall ensure that, on at least 50 fishing voyages, observers shall be present on board fishing vessels deploying either semi-pelagic trawls or separator trawls under the conditions laid down in Article 2. </inglise>
